{%- set log_val = account_log_level | upper %}
{%- set metric_val = account_metric_level | upper %}
{%- set trace_val = account_trace_level | upper | replace(' ', '_') %}
{%- set sql_trace_val = account_sql_trace_query_text | upper %}

## Telemetry Configuration Summary

| Parameter | Value |
|-----------|-------|
{%- if log_val == 'OFF' and metric_val == 'NONE' and trace_val == 'OFF' and sql_trace_val == 'OFF' %}
| Event Table | _(not set — all telemetry disabled)_ |
{%- else %}
| Event Table | `SNOWFLAKE.TELEMETRY.EVENTS` |
{%- endif %}
| Log Level | `{{ log_val }}` |
| Metric Level | `{{ metric_val }}` |
| Trace Level | `{{ trace_val }}` |
| SQL Trace Query Text | `{{ sql_trace_val }}` |

{%- if log_val == 'OFF' and trace_val != 'OFF' %}

> **Warning**: You have selected `TRACE_LEVEL = {{ trace_val }}` but `LOG_LEVEL = OFF`. Traces will **not** be captured until `LOG_LEVEL` is set to a value other than `OFF`.
{%- endif %}

### What Will Be Captured

{%- if log_val != 'OFF' %}
- **Logs**: Messages at `{{ log_val }}` severity and above from handler code
{%- else %}
- **Logs**: Disabled — no log messages will be captured
{%- endif %}
{%- if metric_val == 'ALL' %}
- **Metrics**: Execution metrics (CPU, memory, duration) from handler code
{%- else %}
- **Metrics**: Disabled — no execution metrics will be collected
{%- endif %}
{%- if trace_val != 'OFF' and log_val != 'OFF' %}
- **Traces**: Execution spans with start/end timestamps, status, and query context
{%- elif trace_val != 'OFF' and log_val == 'OFF' %}
- **Traces**: Configured as `{{ trace_val }}` but **blocked** because `LOG_LEVEL` is `OFF`
{%- else %}
- **Traces**: Disabled — no trace spans will be captured
{%- endif %}
{%- if sql_trace_val == 'ON' %}
- **SQL Text**: SQL statements (up to 1024 chars) will be included in trace data
{%- else %}
- **SQL Text**: SQL statements will not be included in trace data
{%- endif %}
